pr_body:
# Description

> :memo: A unified top-down model that extends existing `MaskRCNNModel` to support panoptic segmentation 
## Type of change
- [x] A new research paper code implementation

## Tests

> :memo: Please describe the tests that you ran to verify your changes.

> `python -m official.vision.beta.projects.panoptic_maskrcnn.modeling.panoptic_maskrcnn_model_test` 
Along with the existing `MaskRCNNModel` test cases, I have included additional test cases for

> For instance heads and stuff segmentation heads
>* shared/separate backbones
>* shared/separate decoders

- [x] I have signed the [Contributor License Agreement](https://github.com/tensorflow/models/wiki/Contributor-License-Agreements).
